channel.title: I need help adding shops & deleting objects in a 530 Server please
channel.description: Okay here is the server source + client I am using: Xenorune 530. I can't find anywhere's online where to edit the shops or even to add or remove a object in this type of 530 server. It seems as if it is a rare game frame and very few people know how to use it. Whenever I follow a 508 or a 562 guide or even a 317 guide the files such as client.java and actionsender.java and frames.java are missing but there are other ones instead, such as objectmanager.java or shop-packets.java but they are all names and put together slightly different. If anyone can help me with this it would be greatly appreciated! I will Rep + to whomever walks me through this nightmare.
